text: São José do Rio Preto () is a city in the state of São Paulo, Brazil. The city is in the north/northwest part of the state, with a distance of 440 km (273 mi) from São Paulo, and 700 km (435 mi) from Brasília. In 2021, about 469,173 people lived in the city, making it the 52th biggest in Brazil. ==References== Category:Cities in São Paulo (state)
